    </div>
    <span class="post-cat">Software Review · Content Optimisation</span>
    <h1>Rankability Review 2026: $49/mo NLP Content Tool — Worth It?</h1>
    <p class="description">Rankability is the underdog content optimiser that quietly does NLP scoring better than tools 2× its price. It is also <strong>still an editor that needs a writer behind it, an SEO research tool beside it, and a publishing workflow after it</strong>. After 30 days of side-by-side testing against Surfer and Clearscope, here is the honest 2026 verdict.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">SG</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/siddharth-gangal/">Siddharth Gangal</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Founder · theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
