        <h2 id="faq">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What is Rankability?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Rankability is a content optimisation platform built around NLP scoring against ranking competitors. It generates SEO briefs, scores draft content against top-ranking pages, surfaces semantic keywords, and includes AI writing assistance. It is most often compared with Surfer SEO and Clearscope.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How much does Rankability cost in 2026?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Starter is $49/mo, Pro is $99/mo, Agency is $199/mo. Annual billing offers a discount. Higher tiers add more reports per month, more team seats, white-label briefs, and increased AI writing credits. A free trial is available on most plans.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Is Rankability better than Surfer SEO?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Rankability is significantly cheaper than Surfer at the entry tier ($49 vs $119) and many users prefer its cleaner scoring methodology. Surfer has more features (SERP analyser, audit, AI Outline) and a larger ecosystem. For pure content scoring on a budget, Rankability wins on value. For an all-in-one workflow with audit and outline, Surfer wins on breadth.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Does Rankability write content for you?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Partially. Rankability includes AI writing assistance that drafts paragraphs and full articles based on the brief. You still need to edit, fact-check, add original analysis, and publish manually. It does not have an autonomous publishing layer.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Is Rankability worth it for small businesses?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>For small businesses with an in-house writer or agency support: yes — the Starter plan at $49/mo is excellent value. For small businesses without writers, the real cost of producing content with Rankability is $1,500–$5,000/mo once writers and editing are factored in.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
